===Noun===
A '''rhythmic gesture''' is a [[durational pattern]] which, in contrast to a [[rhythmic unit]], does not occupy a period of time equivalent to a [[pulse (music)|pulse]] or pulses on an underlying [[metric level]].

See: [[rhythm]]

